Created by Page Schmidt and Kevin Green
Final Project for COMP 271 (Data Structures)
Loyola University, Fall 2010

**Drink recipes retrieved from http://www.idrink.com**

Application Features:

-Keeps a library of drink recipes/their required ingredients.

-Allows user to choose the ingredients they currently have
and adds them to an inventory.

-Returns a list of recipes the user can make with the
ingredients they have.

-Returns a list of recipes the user could make with
the purchase of one additional ingredient.

-"Random Drink" feature displays a random recipe from
the application's library.

-User can also browse the library of drink recipes.